{"id":263641,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-十八大期间山东强拆受害人孔大华被强制/","date":"2012-11-17T22:31:37Z","modified":"2012-11-17T22:31:37Z","title":"维权网 | 十八大期间山东强拆受害人孔大华被强制旅游","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员欧蕊报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>点</span><span>，山东临沂暴力强拆受害人孔大华“被旅游”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天后由所在单位书记送回家。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据知情人透露：孔大华是山东临沂市政府实施野蛮暴力强拆的众多受害人之一。他是一名共产党员，一直以自己是一名党员为骄傲。在遭遇临沂市政府非法暴力强拆后的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>年中，始终坚信党中央“依法治国”、“依法行政”的治国方针。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>几年来孔大华依法诉讼、不断到上级有关部门上访，问题不但没有解决反而成为当地政府的维稳对象。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>，十八大召开的前一天，为防止孔大华赴京上访，地方政府安排他所在的单位书记将他带往湖南</span><span> </span><span>“旅游”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>直到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>十八大闭幕，孔大华“被旅游”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天后才被允许返回临沂。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3261761693877267633?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\